**[The Spoils of War — Shield Examination Begins]**
- Vukradin opens with the framing question before any game content begins, flagging it as OOC intent before roleplay.

**Vukradin** — *asking OOC about the shield's appearance before roleplaying it*
> "I would like to ask the DM a question."
> "How different does this shield look from a standard It's N-Shield."
> "This is out of… I'm asking you outside of my character, and then I will roleplay it."

**GM** — *responding to the OOC question*
> "Oh, we need to describe the shield, the plus one shield?"
> "I have… I have… I have… I have tables for that. You're going to have to give me a sec."

